  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，我猜你已经听说过叛逃USEC了吧？他们的头儿似乎又在恐吓当地人了，他们开始逐渐从他们的小基地扩散开了。另一位商人告诉我，他派了一名信使去尝试跟他们谈判，但结果可想而知，他们很冷血地直接了结了他。这帮人还没有打搅到我的团队……至少目前为止还没有。我想提前避免这种情况的发生，他们太具有攻击性了。我知道你是这方面的专家，所以我现在请求你帮我个忙。干掉这帮小丑，同时把他们的装备带回来。只要是他们身上穿的东西就行，衣服服装或装备护甲都可以，别担心，你可以留着他们的枪支弹药。但是我需要你在一定条件下进行这次行动——穿着BEAR干员的装备，这样在送他们上黄泉路之前能清楚到底是谁痛下的杀手。能做到吗？\n\nBEAR装备：\n - 6B47头盔 或 BEAR棒球帽\n - Bagariy 或 TV-110 或 TV-115防弹板\n - 任意AK系列步枪",
    "en": "Hey, I assume you have heard about the rogue USECs already? Their leaders seem to be terrorizing the locals again, they started to spread out further from their little base. Another dealer told me that he sent a messenger or something to negotiate with them but they just killed him in cold blood. They have not disturbed my group... yet. I want to avoid that, they are just too aggressive. I know you are an expert at this, so I will ask you for that favor now. Get rid of these clowns and while you are at it, bring me their gear. Just what they were wearing is fine, armor or rigs, whatever, you can keep the guns and ammo don't worry. But I want you to do it under certain conditions - Dress up as a BEAR operative, so they clearly see who takes them out. They should see the very thing that they hate the most before they get sent into afterlife. Can you manage it?\n\nBEAR gear :\n - 6B47 Helmets / BEAR Baseballcap\n - Bagariy / TV-110 / TV-115 Plate Carrier\n - An AK-Type Weapon"
  },
